vote.title: An ordinance granting renewal of a private license to Ponte Gadea Compass, LLC, for the use of a total of approximately 6,215 square feet of land to occupy, maintain and utilize two existing railroad crossing tracks and three traffic signal poles on portions of Jefferson Boulevard right-of-way located near its intersection with 14th Street - Revenue: General Fund $3,100.00 annually, plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
